decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Ting-Tings-perform-live-Photo-by-Pedro-Gomes_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Ting-Tings-perform-live-Photo-by-Pedro-Gomes_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Ting-Tings-perform-live-Photo-by-Pedro-Gomes_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Ting-Tings-perform-live-Photo-by-Pedro-Gomes_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Ting-Tings-perform-live-Photo-by-Pedro-Gomes_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Ting-Tings-perform-live-Photo-by-Pedro-Gomes_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ting-tings">Ting Tings</a>预告了一首乡村风格的新曲目，名为“Dance On The Wire”——请查看下面的预告片。</p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/indie-sleaze-revival-the-maccabees-the-horrors-white-heat-3162006"><b>“有一种乐观的感觉”：00 年代独立音乐如何大规模卷土重来</b></a></li></ul><p>乐队上周在社交媒体上分享了这段剪辑，这首歌似乎倾向于乡村音乐，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artsits/post-malone">波斯特·马龙</a>等艺术家都在制作乡村音乐专辑。</p><p>由凯蒂·怀特 (Katie White) 和朱尔斯·德·马蒂诺 (Jules De Martino) 组成的独立流行二人组凭借首张热门歌曲《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v1c2OfAzDTI">那不是我的名字》(That&#39;s Not My Name</a> ) 登上了英国排行榜的榜首。这首歌于 2008 年发行后迅速走红，迄今为止销量已超过 100 万张。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-ting-tings-respond-to-thats-not-my-name-going-viral-on-tiktok-were-thrilled-3162919">早在 2022 年，这首歌就再次走红——这次是在 TikTok 上，</a>因为它成为巨石强森、德鲁·巴里摩尔等人的视频配乐。</p><p>怀特在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2022/music/news/ting-tings-thats-not-my-name-tiktok-interview-1235181456/"><i>《综艺》</i></a>采访时谈到了这首歌当时的复兴，他说：“我们[不擅长]社交媒体。我从家人那里得知这件事正在发生。”</p><p> “我不认为 TikTok 真的适合我们，”这位歌手兼吉他手补充道，“但现在我们可能会在下一张专辑中使用它。”</p><p> “我们很兴奋，”德马蒂诺补充道。 “看到人们与我们的歌曲互动真是太棒了。在我们职业生涯的早期，有人说：“你写了一首将继续流传下去的歌曲。”他们是对的，这种情况一直在发生。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4oJmCfN-Mh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.